    <item>
      <title>特朗普对美国贸易伙伴征收全面关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/live-blog/2025-02-01/trump-imposes-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024 年 12 月 18 日星期三，拖拉机拖车从加拿大进入美国华盛顿州布莱恩的太平洋公路边境口岸。加拿大对美国的贸易顺差帮助这个北方国家避免了更大的整体赤字，凸显了其最大贸易伙伴的重要性，因为当选总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁要征收高额关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/live-blog/2025-02-01/trump-imposes-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 22:07:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在贸易战中对中国、加拿大、墨西哥征收关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/trump-hits-china-canada-mexico-with-tariffs-to-open-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统打响了关税战的第一枪，对加拿大和墨西哥征收 25% 的普遍关税，对中国征收 10% 的普遍关税 — — 这标志着特朗普将对外国盟友和对手发动一波贸易攻势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/trump-hits-china-canada-mexico-with-tariffs-to-open-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 22:06:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普签署对加拿大和墨西哥征收 25% 关税、对中国征收 10% 关税的协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/trump-signs-25-tariffs-on-canada-and-mexico-10-on-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国官员透露，美国将对加拿大和墨西哥的出口产品征收25%的关税，并对中国产品征收10%的关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/trump-signs-25-tariffs-on-canada-and-mexico-10-on-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 22:05:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Dollar General 要求商店让 ICE 与员工和客户对话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/dollar-general-tells-stores-to-let-ice-talk-to-staff-customers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元通用百货公司 (Dollar General Corp.) 正在指示商店经理让前往其门店的移民执法人员与员工和顾客交谈，这表明公司正准备就特朗普政府的优先事项进行合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/dollar-general-tells-stores-to-let-ice-talk-to-staff-customers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 21:51:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普特使和微笑的马杜罗重启委内瑞拉关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/trump-s-envoy-and-a-smiling-maduro-reset-venezuela-relations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一次旋风之旅中，唐纳德·特朗普总统的特使推翻了拜登政府多年来在委内瑞拉的外交政策，并与委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗重新开始，这一转变可能会对从移民到石油市场产生影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/trump-s-envoy-and-a-smiling-maduro-reset-venezuela-relations</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 21:22:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大准备对特朗普关税采取报复措施，重新考虑对美国的依赖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/canada-poised-to-retaliate-against-trump-tariffs-while-rethinking-us-reliance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大即将出台升级的报复性反关税，试图让美国人反对唐纳德·特朗普总统对加拿大商品征收 25% 的关税，这一威胁促使美国重新考虑对南方邻国的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/canada-poised-to-retaliate-against-trump-tariffs-while-rethinking-us-reliance</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 18:31:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将首次对全球实施多项关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/trump-set-to-launch-first-of-many-volleys-in-his-new-tariff-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统正准备打响关税战的第一枪，并迫不及待地想要预演下一枪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/trump-set-to-launch-first-of-many-volleys-in-his-new-tariff-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 13:33:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉面临的挑战日益严峻，巴西国会选出新领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/brazil-s-congress-picks-new-leaders-as-lula-s-challenges-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦已经面临食品价格上涨、投资者怀疑情绪加深和支持率下降的问题。现在他又面临另一个挑战：国会领导层的变动将考验他驾驭该国保守立法机构的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/brazil-s-congress-picks-new-leaders-as-lula-s-challenges-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国公民在最新加沙人质囚犯交换行动中获释</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/fourth-hostage-prisoner-swap-underway-as-gaza-ceasefire-holds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[星期六早上，第四次人质与囚犯交换计划顺利进行，以色列和哈马斯遵守加沙停火第一阶段的协议，包括重新开放通往埃及的拉法口岸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-01/fourth-hostage-prisoner-swap-underway-as-gaza-ceasefire-holds</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 07:44:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>根据最新交换协议，哈马斯将于周六释放三名男性人质</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-02-01/hamas-to-release-3-male-hostages-israel-to-release-dozens-of-palestinian-prisoners-under-ceasefire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汗尤尼斯，加沙地带（美联社）——周六，加沙停火协议实现了迄今为止最顺利的以色列人质与巴勒斯坦囚犯交换，而在停火协议难度大得多的第二阶段谈判开始前两天，至关重要的拉法边境口岸重新开放。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-02-01/hamas-to-release-3-male-hostages-israel-to-release-dozens-of-palestinian-prisoners-under-ceasefire</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 05:31:10 GMT</pubDate>
